proposal: Diving into the world of crypto with a focus on privacy? We get it. With 136 holders on the ETH network, you're carving a niche for privacy in trading and liquidity leasing. How about amplifying this vision with tools that let your community deploy their own DEX or engage in a blockchain-based lottery? A perfect match for privacy enthusiasts looking to expand their horizons. Let's make privacy not just a choice, but a lifestyle.
